original: Dahllöf, Nils Oskar, rektor, Växjö, £. 2W7/9S i Vänersborg av banm. N. W. D. o. Emma Olsson. G. 1. m. Dagmar Eriksson, d. 37; 2. 39 m. Gunvor Maj Elisabeth Halil. — Stud:ex. i Vänersborg 13, fil. mag. i Upps. 19, fil. lic. i Gbg 28 o. fil. dr där 31. Res. t. Frankr. o. Ital. 31. E. o. lär. v. olika läroanst. 18-29, adj. i latin o. grek. v. Karol. lärov. i Örebro 29, lektor i samma ämnen v. Kristianstads h. a. 1. 31, rektor v. Växjö h. a. 1. sed. 35. Skr.: Tempora o. modi h. Columella (griadiiaMh.). RNO.
translated: Dahllöf, Nils Oskar, principal, Växjö, b. 27/9S in Vänersborg to railway manager N.W.D. and Emma Olsson. Married 1st to Dagmar Eriksson, who passed away in 37; married 2nd in 39 to Gunvor Maj Elisabeth Halil. — Graduated from high school in Vänersborg in 13, earned a bachelor's degree from Uppsala University in 19, a master's degree from the University of Gothenburg in 28, and a PhD in 31. Traveled to France and Italy in 31. Taught at various educational institutions from 18-29, served as an adjunct in Latin and Greek at Karolinska Secondary School in Örebro in 29, as a lecturer in the same subjects at Kristianstad High School in 31, and as a principal at Växjö High School from 35 onwards. Author of "Tempora and Moda as in Columella" (thesis). Awarded the Order of the Polar Star.
